Description:

This patchs must be used because wms also uses alaw file extensions as pcm file extension.

 1. Get the source for Asterisk 1.8.3.2 from:
 
 http://downloads.asterisk.org/pub/telephony/asterisk/old-releases/asterisk-1.8.3.2.tar.gz
 
 
 2. Untar the Asterisk 1.8.3.2
 
 $ tar -zxvf asterisk-1.8.3.2.tar.gz
 
 
 3. Add pcm file extension patch
 
 $ patch -p1 -d asterisk-1.8.3.2/ < asterisk-i-pcm-file-extension.patch 
 
 4. Build Asterisk
 
 $ cd asterisk-1.8.3.2
 $ ./configure
 $ make